<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个月也过去一半了，<delay20 />
终于要开始洋溢起<delay8 />圣诞节的气氛了啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多该认真起来，<delay20 />
好好考虑一下该送什么礼物了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />你要是也想送别人礼物的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不要忘记得把礼物包装好了再送出去哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送没包装好的礼物，<delay8 />是会糟蹋掉节日氛围的！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我记得我小时候，<delay8 />因为特别期待收到礼物，<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以至于在圣诞节的早上<delay20 />
起得比谁都早<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那兴奋难耐的心情，我一生难忘。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过如今<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />轮到自己送礼物给别人了，<delay8 />
倒也挺令人兴奋的呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />广场上<delay8 />布置了一棵巨大的圣诞树呢～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来这座<tag a="110" b="32" />也<delay8 />完全
沉浸在了圣诞节的气氛中啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也<delay8 />趁现在多拍几张照片吧！<delay40 />
虽说这种事常常等到事后才会察觉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但留下美好回忆<delay8 />真的很重要哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>